node.title: Commuter chaos in Auckland as debris blocks road, car breaks down on Harbour Bridge
node.description: It could be a stressful morning for Aucklanders.
node.content: ["It could be a stressful morning for Aucklanders looking to commute around the city with two road incidents causing traffic delays on Wednesday.", "Shortly before 11am, Waka Kotahi tweeted a breakdown on the Harbour Bridge could cause delays for citybound travellers.", "https://twitter.com/WakaKotahiAkNth/status/1475946486521339912", "There was also drama on the road further south when a piece of debris partly blocked a southbound lane on State Highway 1.", "\"Due to debris part-blocking the right southbound lane after Hill Rd off-ramp, expect delays,\" Waka Kotahi tweeted.", "The transport agency later said the debris had been cleared, but warned Aucklanders to expect delays as congestion eases.", "https://twitter.com/WakaKotahiAkNth/status/1475946885458374659", "\u00a0"]
